      "disable": "<p>@Check[Warfare Lore|dc:16] to engage the mortar safety switches, @Check[thievery|dc:18] to jam the auto-loading mechanisms so no more ammunition can be cycled, or @Check[athletics|dc:20] to push the tubes out of alignment such that the projectiles no longer threaten the battlefield</p>",
